msgid "Lyrics"
msgstr "歌詞"

msgid "Synced Lyrics"
msgstr "同步歌詞"

msgid "Time-synced lyrics fetched from lrclib.net — free, no account needed"
msgstr "從 lrclib.net 取得的時間同步歌詞 — 免費，無需帳號"

msgid "Enable Synced Lyrics"
msgstr "啟用同步歌詞"

msgid "Fetch and display scrolling lyrics that follow the current playback position"
msgstr "取得並顯示跟隨目前播放位置捲動的歌詞"

msgid "How to Use Lyrics"
msgstr "如何使用歌詞"

msgid "Lyrics are tied to each player tab independently — Spotify and Firefox each remember their own setting"
msgstr "歌詞與每個播放器分頁獨立關聯 — Spotify 和 Firefox 各自記住自己的設定"

msgid "Start playing a song"
msgstr "開始播放一首歌曲"

msgid "Open the popup player"
msgstr "開啟彈出播放器"

msgid "Triple-click the album art to show lyrics"
msgstr "三下點擊專輯封面以顯示歌詞"

msgid "Single-click the lyrics panel to go back"
msgstr "單擊歌詞面板以返回"

msgid "Triple-click again to re-open"
msgstr "再次三下點擊以重新開啟歌詞"

msgid "Open any media player or browser tab (Spotify, YouTube Music, VLC, Rhythmbox…) and play a track so it appears in the panel."
msgstr "開啟任意媒體播放器或瀏覽器分頁（Spotify、YouTube Music、VLC、Rhythmbox…），播放一首曲目使其顯示在面板中。"

msgid "Click the media controller icon in the top panel to open the popup. You'll see the album art, track title, and playback controls."
msgstr "點擊頂部面板的媒體控制器圖示以開啟彈出視窗。您將看到專輯封面、曲目標題和播放控制項。"

msgid "Click the album art three times in quick succession. The cover image will be replaced by the lyrics panel, which scrolls automatically in time with the music."
msgstr "快速連續點擊專輯封面三次。封面圖片將被歌詞面板取代，歌詞面板會隨音樂自動捲動。"

msgid "Tap anywhere on the lyrics panel once to dismiss it and return to the album art — vinyl or normal cover, whichever that app uses."
msgstr "在歌詞面板上任意位置單擊一次即可關閉並返回專輯封面 — 黑膠唱片或一般封面，取決於該應用程式使用哪種。"

msgid "You can toggle the lyrics panel as many times as you like. Each player tab remembers independently whether lyrics are open."
msgstr "您可以隨意多次切換歌詞面板。每個播放器分頁會獨立記住歌詞是否處於開啟狀態。"

msgid "Lyrics Behaviour"
msgstr "歌詞行為"

msgid "What happens behind the scenes"
msgstr "背景中發生的事情"

msgid "Lyrics details & edge cases"
msgstr "歌詞詳情與邊緣情況"

msgid "What to expect when the lyrics panel is open"
msgstr "歌詞面板開啟時的預期效果"

msgid ""
"Source\n"
"  • Lyrics are fetched from lrclib.net — a free, open public database\n"
"  • No account or API key is required; the request is made silently in the background\n"
"\n"
"Display\n"
"  • The active lyric line is shown larger and centred in the panel\n"
"  • The line above and below are shown at medium size; all others fade out\n"
"  • The panel scrolls smoothly so the active line is always in view\n"
"\n"
"Track changes\n"
"  • When a new song starts while the lyrics panel is open, the view clears\n"
"    and new lyrics are fetched automatically\n"
"  • If no lyrics are found, a “No lyrics found” message is shown\n"
"\n"
"Multiple players\n"
"  • Each player tab (Spotify, YouTube, VLC…) has its own independent\n"
"    lyrics toggle — opening lyrics for one player does not affect any other\n"
"  • Switching tabs restores the correct view (lyrics or album art) for\n"
"    the player you switch to\n"
"\n"
"Seeking\n"
"  • When you seek forward or backward, the highlighted line jumps\n"
"    instantly to the correct position"
msgstr ""
"來源\n"
"  • 歌詞從 lrclib.net 取得 — 這是一個免費的開放公共資料庫\n"
"  • 無需帳號或 API 金鑰；請求在背景靜默進行\n"
"\n"
"顯示\n"
"  • 目前啟用的歌詞行在面板中放大並置中顯示\n"
"  • 上下相鄰行以中等大小顯示；其餘行淡出\n"
"  • 面板平滑捲動，使啟用行始終在可視範圍內\n"
"\n"
"曲目切換\n"
"  • 當歌詞面板開啟時新歌曲開始播放，畫面將清空\n"
"    並自動取得新歌詞\n"
"  • 如果找不到歌詞，將顯示「找不到歌詞」訊息\n"
"\n"
"多播放器\n"
"  • 每個播放器分頁（Spotify、YouTube、VLC…）都有其獨立的\n"
"    歌詞開關 — 為一個播放器開啟歌詞不會影響其他播放器\n"
"  • 切換分頁會為切換到的播放器還原正確的畫面（歌詞或專輯封面）\n"
"\n"
"定位\n"
"  • 向前或向後跳轉時，反白顯示的歌詞行會\n"
"    立即跳轉到正確位置"

msgid "Album Art Click Actions"
msgstr "專輯封面點擊操作"

msgid "Summary of what each click pattern does on the album art cover"
msgstr "各點擊方式在專輯封面上的操作說明"

msgid "Single click"
msgstr "單擊"

msgid "When lyrics are showing: closes the lyrics panel and returns to the album art"
msgstr "顯示歌詞時：關閉歌詞面板並返回專輯封面"

msgid "Double click"
msgstr "雙擊"

msgid "Toggles the spinning vinyl record effect for that specific app (remembered independently per app)"
msgstr "切換該特定應用程式的黑膠唱片旋轉效果（每個應用程式獨立記住）"

msgid "Triple click"
msgstr "三擊"

msgid "Toggles the synced lyrics panel for the current player tab (remembered independently per player)"
msgstr "切換目前播放器分頁的同步歌詞面板（每個播放器獨立記住）"

msgid "Data Source"
msgstr "資料來源"

msgid "Where lyrics come from"
msgstr "歌詞來自何處"

msgid "lrclib.net"
msgstr "lrclib.net"

msgid "Free, open-source time-synced lyrics database — no sign-up, no tracking, no ads"
msgstr "免費開源的時間同步歌詞資料庫 — 無需註冊，不追蹤，無廣告"

msgid "Privacy note"
msgstr "隱私說明"

msgid "A request containing the track title, artist, album and duration is sent to lrclib.net when you open the lyrics panel. No personal data or user identifiers are included."
msgstr "開啟歌詞面板時，會向 lrclib.net 傳送包含曲目標題、藝術家、專輯和時長的請求。不包含任何個人資料或使用者識別碼。"

msgid "Fetching lyrics…"
msgstr "正在取得歌詞…"

msgid "No lyrics found"
msgstr "找不到歌詞"